(39848, 0, 0, 0, 0, '<The air hangs silent as you approach.>'), -- A Desperate Bargain
(38347, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Gods, what is that stench?! $B$BThis disguise had better work!'), -- Stealth by Seaweed
